<lb n="0350c08" ed="X"/><lb n="0699b03" ed="R128"/><p xml:id="pX74p0350c0801">究竟虗空十方界<note place="inline">至</note>現斯苦行摧異道。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0350c09" ed="X"/><lb n="0699b04" ed="R128"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="2" type="其他">十一斷一切疑功德</cb:mulu><head>十一斷一切疑功德</head>
<lb n="0350c10" ed="X"/><lb n="0699b05" ed="R128"/><p xml:id="pX74p0350c1001">或持彼戒為世師<note place="inline">至</note>方便皆令住佛道。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0350c11" ed="X"/><lb n="0699b06" ed="R128"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="2" type="其他">十二令入種種行功德</cb:mulu><head>十二令入種種行功德</head>
<lb n="0350c12" ed="X"/><lb n="0699b07" ed="R128"/><p xml:id="pX74p0350c1201">或現上服以嚴身<note place="inline">至</note>然後捨去無知者。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0350c13" ed="X"/><lb n="0699b08" ed="R128"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="2" type="其他">十三當來世生妙智功德</cb:mulu><head>十三當來世生妙智功德</head>
<lb n="0350c14" ed="X"/><lb n="0699b09" ed="R128"/><p xml:id="pX74p0350c1401">如來無礙智所見<note place="inline">至</note>種種教化令成就。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0350c15" ed="X"/><lb n="0699b10" ed="R128"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="2" type="其他">十四隨其勝解示現功德</cb:mulu><head>十四隨其勝解示現功德</head>
<lb n="0350c16" ed="X"/><lb n="0699b11" ed="R128"/><p xml:id="pX74p0350c1601">譬如幻師善幻術<note place="inline">至</note>靡不於中現其像。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0350c17" ed="X"/><lb n="0699b12" ed="R128"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="2" type="其他">十五無量所依調伏有情加行功德</cb:mulu><head>十五無量所依調伏有情加行功德</head>
<lb n="0350c18" ed="X"/><lb n="0699b13" ed="R128"/><p xml:id="pX74p0350c1801">譬如淨日放千光<note place="inline">至</note>普使滅除三毒火。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0350c19" ed="X"/><lb n="0699b14" ed="R128"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="2" type="其他">十六平等法身波羅蜜多成滿功德</cb:mulu><head>十六平等法身波羅蜜多成滿功德</head>
<lb n="0350c20" ed="X"/><lb n="0699b15" ed="R128"/><p xml:id="pX74p0350c2001">如來清淨妙法身<note place="inline">至</note>當於佛體如是觀。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0350c21" ed="X"/><lb n="0699b16" ed="R128"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="2" type="其他">十七隨其勝解示現差別佛土功德</cb:mulu><head>十七隨其勝解示現差別佛土功德</head>
<lb n="0350c22" ed="X"/><lb n="0699b17" ed="R128"/><p xml:id="pX74p0350c2201">三界有無一切法<note place="inline">至</note>無有依空而住者。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0350c23" ed="X"/><lb n="0699b18" ed="R128"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="2" type="其他">十八三種佛身六住無分限功德</cb:mulu><head>十八三種佛身六住無分限功德</head>
<lb n="0350c24" ed="X"/><lb n="0700a01" ed="R128"/><p xml:id="pX74p0350c2401">大海摩尼無量色<note place="inline">至</note>隨應而現無所住。</p></cb:div>
<pb n="0351a" ed="X" xml:id="X74.1470.0351a"/>
<lb n="0351a01" ed="X"/><lb n="0700a02" ed="R128"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="2" type="其他">十九究竟功德等三種功德</cb:mulu><head>十九究竟功德等三種功德</head>
<lb n="0351a02" ed="X"/><lb n="0700a03" ed="R128"/><p xml:id="pX74p0351a0201">虗空真如及實際<note place="inline">至</note>可以顯示於如來。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0351a03" ed="X"/><lb n="0700a04" ed="R128"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="2" type="其他">後結德無盡</cb:mulu><head>後結德無盡</head>
<lb n="0351a04" ed="X"/><lb n="0700a05" ed="R128"/><p xml:id="pX74p0351a0401">剎塵心念可數知<note place="inline">至</note>慎勿於此懷疑念。</p>
<lb n="0351a05" ed="X"/><lb n="0700a06" ed="R128"/><lg xml:id="lgX74p0351a0501"><l>願共諸眾生，<caesura/>往生華藏海，<caesura/>極樂淨土中。</l></lg>
<lb n="0351a06" ed="X"/><lb n="0700a07" ed="R128"/><list rend="no-marker"><item xml:id="itemX74p0351a0601">至心歸命禮大方廣佛華嚴經華藏世界海本尊毗
<lb n="0351a07" ed="X"/><lb n="0700a08" ed="R128"/>盧遮那佛。</item>
<lb n="0351a08" ed="X"/><lb n="0700a09" ed="R128"/><item xml:id="itemX74p0351a0801">南無十身無礙毗盧遮那如來道場一切海</item>
<lb n="0351a09" ed="X"/><lb n="0700a10" ed="R128"/><item xml:id="itemX74p0351a0901">南無大方廣佛華嚴經中普賢行願品法門</item></list>
<lb n="0351a10" ed="X"/><lb n="0700a11" ed="R128"/><lg xml:id="lgX74p0351a1001" type="regular"><l>十方盡歸命，<caesura/>滅罪增淨信，<caesura/>願生華藏海。</l>
<lb n="0351a11" ed="X"/><lb n="0700a12" ed="R128"/><l>極樂淨土中。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb n="0351a12" ed="X"/><lb n="0700a13" ed="R128"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="2" type="其他">入不思議解脫境界普賢行願品</cb:mulu><head>●入不思議解脫境界普賢行願品</head>
<lb n="0351a13" ed="X"/><lb n="0700a14" ed="R128"/><p xml:id="pX74p0351a1301">經云爾時普賢菩薩<note place="inline">至</note>十者普皆迴向。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0351a14" ed="X"/><lb n="0700a15" ed="R128"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="2" type="其他">第一禮敬諸佛</cb:mulu><head>第一禮敬諸佛</head>
<lb n="0351a15" ed="X"/><lb n="0700a16" ed="R128"/><p xml:id="pX74p0351a1501">經云善財白言大聖<note place="inline">至</note>身語意業無有疲厭。</p>
<lb n="0351a16" ed="X"/><lb n="0700a17" ed="R128"/><p xml:id="pX74p0351a1601">禮敬<note n="0351a1601" resp="CBETA" type="add">已【CB】，巳【卍續】</note><app n="0351a1601"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CB】">已</lem><rdg wit="【卍續】">巳</rdg></app>，至心歸命禮本尊毗盧遮那佛。</p></cb:div>
