<lb n="0351a18" ed="X"/><lb n="0700b01" ed="R128"/><p xml:id="pX74p0351a1801">復次，善男子！言稱讚如來者<note place="inline">至</note>身語意業無有疲厭。</p>
<lb n="0351a19" ed="X"/><lb n="0700b02" ed="R128"/><p xml:id="pX74p0351a1901">讚歎<note n="0351a1901" resp="CBETA" type="add">已【CB】，巳【卍續】</note><app n="0351a1901"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CB】">已</lem><rdg wit="【卍續】">巳</rdg></app>，至心歸命禮本尊毗盧遮那佛。</p></cb:div>
