<pb n="0351b" ed="X" xml:id="X74.1470.0351b"/>
<lb n="0351b01" ed="X"/><lb n="0700b08" ed="R128"/><p xml:id="pX74p0351b0101">懺悔<note n="0351b0101" resp="CBETA" type="add">已【CB】，巳【卍續】</note><app n="0351b0101"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CB】">已</lem><rdg wit="【卍續】">巳</rdg></app>，至心歸命禮本尊毗盧遮那佛。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0351b02" ed="X"/><lb n="0700b09" ed="R128"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="2" type="其他">第五隨喜功德</cb:mulu><head>第五隨喜功德</head>
<lb n="0351b03" ed="X"/><lb n="0700b10" ed="R128"/><p xml:id="pX74p0351b0301">復次，男子！言隨喜功德者<note place="inline">至</note>身語意業無有疲厭。</p>
<lb n="0351b04" ed="X"/><lb n="0700b11" ed="R128"/><p xml:id="pX74p0351b0401">隨喜<note n="0351b0401" resp="CBETA" type="add">已【CB】，巳【卍續】</note><app n="0351b0401"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CB】">已</lem><rdg wit="【卍續】">巳</rdg></app>，至心歸命禮本尊毗盧遮那佛。</p></cb:div>
